Akwai kuri&#39;a na Yahudawa yanka ta &#39;Yan Salibiyyar a Isra&#39;ila. &gt; Akwai wani thriving al&#39;umma a Gaza birnin daga wajen 1200-1500. &gt; Yahudawa sun kasance mafiya yawa a Urushalima daga 1870 ko haka, dole.
